11#include "call/rtp_stream_receiver_controller.h"
12
13#include <memory>
14
15#include "rtc_base/logging.h"
16
17namespace webrtc {
18
19RtpStreamReceiverController::Receiver::Receiver(
20 RtpStreamReceiverController* controller,
21 uint32_t ssrc,
22 RtpPacketSinkInterface* sink)
23 : controller_(controller), sink_(sink) {
24 const bool sink_added = controller_->AddSink(ssrc, sink_);
25 if (!sink_added) {
26 RTC_LOG(LS_ERROR)
27 << "RtpStreamReceiverController::Receiver::Receiver: Sink "
28 "could not be added for SSRC="
29 << ssrc << ".";
30 }
31}
32
33RtpStreamReceiverController::Receiver::~Receiver() {
34 // Don't require return value > 0, since for RTX we currently may
35 // have multiple Receiver objects with the same sink.
36 // TODO(nisse): Consider adding a DCHECK when RtxReceiveStream is wired up.
37 controller_->RemoveSink(sink_);
38}
39
40RtpStreamReceiverController::RtpStreamReceiverController() {}
41
42RtpStreamReceiverController::~RtpStreamReceiverController() = default;
43
44std::unique_ptr<RtpStreamReceiverInterface>
45RtpStreamReceiverController::CreateReceiver(uint32_t ssrc,
46 RtpPacketSinkInterface* sink) {
47 return std::make_unique<Receiver>(this, ssrc, sink);
48}
49
50bool RtpStreamReceiverController::OnRtpPacket(const RtpPacketReceived& packet) {
51 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(&demuxer_sequence_);
52 return demuxer_.OnRtpPacket(packet);
53}
54
55bool RtpStreamReceiverController::AddSink(uint32_t ssrc,
56 RtpPacketSinkInterface* sink) {
57 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(&demuxer_sequence_);
58 return demuxer_.AddSink(ssrc, sink);
59}
60
61size_t RtpStreamReceiverController::RemoveSink(
62 const RtpPacketSinkInterface* sink) {
63 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(&demuxer_sequence_);
64 return demuxer_.RemoveSink(sink);
65}
66
67} // namespace webrtc
